  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mewseum: Masterpieces</strong> is a relaxing game where you can solve hundreds of puzzles while revealing unique masterpieces. Unwind to the sound of a beautiful piano with classical music or listen to your own favorite audio while playing. The puzzles range from easy to medium difficulty, ensuring a smooth and frustration-free experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧩How to Play:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is to paint squares and/or rectangles within the grid while following two simple rules:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each painted section must contain exactly one number.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number indicates the exact size of the section you need to paint.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/a6243f831ffc054be3397bca4e9da573.poster.avif?t=1773256060\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/a6243f831ffc054be3397bca4e9da573.webm?t=1773256060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/a6243f831ffc054be3397bca4e9da573.mp4?t=1773256060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨<strong>Explore Art History… with Cats!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover reimagined versions of iconic paintings, where cats take center stage in some of the most famous artworks in history. The featured paintings include: <br>🦪<i>Girl with a Pearl Earring</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👩‍🎨<i>Mona Lisa</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🙀<i>The Scream</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨<i>Starry Night</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡<i>American Gothic</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦵<i>Abaporu</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👫<i>Arnolfini Portrait</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👩‍👧‍👧<i>Las Meninas</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/4e7940bdb63a3d8d37d1a112fe85381c.poster.avif?t=1773256060\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/4e7940bdb63a3d8d37d1a112fe85381c.webm?t=1773256060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/4e7940bdb63a3d8d37d1a112fe85381c.mp4?t=1773256060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮<strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ <strong>Auto-save with Steam Cloud</strong> – pause and continue anytime.<br>✔ <strong>Over 10 hours of content</strong>: Become a true artist as you reveal stunning paintings by solving relaxing and immersive puzzles. Unlock over 80 achievements and complete your collection!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mewseum: Masterpieces</strong> is a relaxing game where you can solve hundreds of puzzles while revealing unique masterpieces. Unwind to the sound of a beautiful piano with classical music or listen to your own favorite audio while playing. The puzzles range from easy to medium difficulty, ensuring a smooth and frustration-free experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧩How to Play:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is to paint squares and/or rectangles within the grid while following two simple rules:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each painted section must contain exactly one number.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number indicates the exact size of the section you need to paint.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/a6243f831ffc054be3397bca4e9da573.poster.avif?t=1773256060\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/a6243f831ffc054be3397bca4e9da573.webm?t=1773256060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/a6243f831ffc054be3397bca4e9da573.mp4?t=1773256060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨<strong>Explore Art History… with Cats!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover reimagined versions of iconic paintings, where cats take center stage in some of the most famous artworks in history. The featured paintings include: <br>🦪<i>Girl with a Pearl Earring</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👩‍🎨<i>Mona Lisa</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🙀<i>The Scream</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨<i>Starry Night</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡<i>American Gothic</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦵<i>Abaporu</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👫<i>Arnolfini Portrait</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👩‍👧‍👧<i>Las Meninas</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/4e7940bdb63a3d8d37d1a112fe85381c.poster.avif?t=1773256060\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/4e7940bdb63a3d8d37d1a112fe85381c.webm?t=1773256060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417690/extras/4e7940bdb63a3d8d37d1a112fe85381c.mp4?t=1773256060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮<strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ <strong>Auto-save with Steam Cloud</strong> – pause and continue anytime.<br>✔ <strong>Over 10 hours of content</strong>: Become a true artist as you reveal stunning paintings by solving relaxing and immersive puzzles. Unlock over 80 achievements and complete your collection!</p>",
